  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **Parse Outcomes (Last 1h)**: 最近 1 小时解析成功/失败计数，按来源类型、parser 和 error tag 拆分。\n- **Fallback Usage (Last 1h)**: 使用了哪些正文抓取 fallback，例如 `exa_contents`、`trafilatura`。\n- **Chunk Count P95**: 每篇文章切分出来的 chunk 数量 P95，不是耗时。\n- **Worker Job Outcomes (Last 1h)**: ingest/reindex/maintenance job 的成功失败数量。\n- **Content Ready Latency P95**: 从文章创建到正文可展示的 P95 耗时；这里的 ready 不等 index 全部完成。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时解析结果。失败时结合 `error_tag` 看是 parse_empty、ingest_failed 还是其他问题。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (input_type, status, parser, error_tag) (increase(notebooklm_ingest_parse_total[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{input_type}} / {{status}} / {{parser}} / {{error_tag}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Parse Outcomes (Last 1h)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时在正文抓取阶段使用的 fallback 次数。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (fallback_type) (increase(notebooklm_ingest_fallback_total[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{fallback_type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Fallback Usage (Last 1h)",
      "type": "barchart"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "每篇文章切分出的 chunk 数量 P95。数值越高，通常说明正文更长或结构更复杂。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, input_type) (rate(notebooklm_ingest_chunk_count_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{input_type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Chunk Count P95",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时 worker job 成功/失败次数。重点关注 `article_ingest` 和 `article_reindex` 的 failed 曲线。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (job_type, status) (increase(notebooklm_jobs_total{job_type=~\"article_ingest|article_reindex|maintenance_cleanup\"}[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job_type}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Worker Job Outcomes (Last 1h)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "从文章创建到正文可展示的 P95 耗时，单位毫秒。这里的 ready 指 `contentReady=true`，不等索引结束。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
